Package pl.project.util

Class MyMap<K,V>

java.lang.Object
pl.project.util.MyMap<K,V>
Type Parameters:
K - The type of the keys in the map.
V - The type of the values in the map.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Map<K,V>
public class MyMap<K,V> extends Object implements Map<K,V>
This class implements a simple map using two lists: one for keys and one for values. It allows adding, removing, retrieving elements by key, and checking if a key exists in the map. The map does not allow null keys or values.
